\frac{1}{3} - \frac{1}{9}+\frac{1}{27}+\cdots+\frac{1}{3}\left(-\frac{1}{3}\right)^{n+1}+\cdots
S=\dfrac{a}{1-r}
a=1/3,
 r=-1/3
S=1/4
-1/3
\frac{1}{3} \sum_{n=0}^\infty \left(-\frac{1}{3}\right)^{n+1} = \frac{1}{3}\sum_{n=0}^\infty (-\frac{1}{3})(-\frac{1}{3})^n =-\frac{1}{9}\sum_{n=0}^\infty \left(-\frac{1}{3}\right)^n =-1/12
\frac{1}{3} \sum \limits_{n=0}^\infty \left(-\frac{1}{3}\right)^n =\frac{1}{3} \frac{1}{1+\frac{1}{3}} =1/4
\sum_{n=0}^\infty \left(-\frac{1}{3}\right)^n
\sum \limits_{n=0}^\infty (-\frac{1}{3})^{n+1}
